&nbsp;<a href="javascript:;" onclick="showWindow(this.id, this.getAttribute('url'), 'get', 0);" id="savephoto_10327037" url="home.php?mod=spacecp&amp;ac=album&amp;op=saveforumphoto&amp;aid=10327037&amp;handlekey=savephoto_10327037">保存到相册</a>

